      <abstract>
        <p>A new Schiff base 4-[(pyridin-3-ylmethylene)amino]phenylhexadecanoate was synthesized and its IR, <sup>1</sup>H NMR, <sup>13</sup>C NMR and MS spectroscopic data are presented.</p>
      </abstract>
